How: Subject identifier; used to mint ppmi:Subject IRI (not mapped to PDON/PMDO).

Subject sex; attach as data property on Subject.

Family history of PD (binary); attach as data property on Subject.
Genetic observation (categorical); store as Observation with literal value; no stable PDON/PMDO class in provided files.
Visit identifier; used to mint ppmi:Visit IRI (e.g., BL, V04, V06).
Visit timestamp; attach to Visit (xsd:gYearMonth or xsd:date, depending on source).
Visit time index; attach to Visit (integer).
Contextual covariate; attach to Visit (recommended: Visit data property).
